{"PageNumber":25,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":1620,"Width":2880,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"title","Text":"#  RBAC: pros & cons","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":216,"Y":308},"LeftTop":{"X":216,"Y":190},"RightBottom":{"X":1204,"Y":308},"RightTop":{"X":1204,"Y":190}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● The total set of roles should be much smaller than the set of subjects","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":527},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":446},"RightBottom":{"X":2621,"Y":527},"RightTop":{"X":2621,"Y":446}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● Hence, storing access rights just for roles is more efficient","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":326,"Y":626},"LeftTop":{"X":326,"Y":546},"RightBottom":{"X":2054,"Y":626},"RightTop":{"X":2054,"Y":546}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● And the overhead for determining if a subject s has a particular right is small","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":827},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":661},"RightBottom":{"X":2601,"Y":827},"RightTop":{"X":2601,"Y":661}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● for all the system needs to do is to determine if one of the roles for s has that access right","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":326,"Y":1003},"LeftTop":{"X":326,"Y":854},"RightBottom":{"X":2636,"Y":1003},"RightTop":{"X":2636,"Y":854}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":5,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"• The main disadvantage of the role-based access control model is that it is not implemented in current operating systems","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":1219},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":1041},"RightBottom":{"X":2630,"Y":1219},"RightTop":{"X":2630,"Y":1041}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}]}